835
00:34:44,360 --> 00:34:45,360
I have no objections.

836
00:34:45,679 --> 00:34:47,520
But I did nothing wrong here.

837
00:34:47,639 --> 00:34:48,760
So I can't apologize.

838
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,600
Nonsense!

839
00:34:49,639 --> 00:34:51,000
Isn't this just absurd?

840
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:52,360
Is this the time to be stubborn?

841
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:53,600
I'm not being stubborn.

842
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:54,600
This is my principle.

843
00:34:58,680 --> 00:35:00,360
Director Liao, Director Liao, you...

844
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,680
I stand with Lin Yiran.

845
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,360
No apology.

846
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:09,080
Director Liao, she doesn't get the consequences.

847
00:35:09,080 --> 00:35:10,640
And... and neither do you!

848
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,600
You're going on about principles too?

849
00:35:12,920 --> 00:35:14,920
Yes, Lin Yiran did say some people

850
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:17,280
cut corners and compete unfairly.

851
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:18,400
But did she name anyone?

852
00:35:19,240 --> 00:35:20,440
Apologize to whom?

853
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:22,200
The things she described,

854
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:24,640
aren't they real in Taohua Town?

855
00:35:24,840 --> 00:35:26,240
What is there to apologize for?

856
00:35:26,560 --> 00:35:28,840
You can't do this, Master.

857
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:30,000
I'm not your master.

858
00:35:30,640 --> 00:35:34,000
Everything has its right and wrong.

859
00:35:35,160 --> 00:35:36,680
She works under me.

860
00:35:37,080 --> 00:35:38,000
If she's wrong,

861
00:35:38,640 --> 00:35:39,880
I won't cover for her.

862
00:35:40,120 --> 00:35:41,200
She's not wrong,

863
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:43,440
so why should I let her be bullied?

864
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:45,000
This...

865
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:47,760
This isn't about who's bullying whom.

866
00:35:48,160 --> 00:35:51,840
Today's matter is no small thing.

867
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:54,920
If Erhu doesn't get the answer he wants,

868
00:35:55,240 --> 00:35:57,320
he'll go to the city, then the province.

869
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,880
If this blows up, no one's getting away.

870
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:04,800
Master, if you don't want to advance,

871
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:06,120
fine.

872
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:10,520
But I'm not like you.

873
00:36:11,560 --> 00:36:14,080
I have no background, no capital.

874
00:36:14,720 --> 00:36:16,880
Getting this far wasn't easy for me.

875
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:18,480
Not easy,

876
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:21,280
but I still can't blur right and wrong.

877
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:23,480
Not easy,

878
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:26,760
but I still can't break my backbone.

879
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:36,960
Lin Yiran, are you coming or not?

880
00:36:37,640 --> 00:36:38,480
Lin Yiran.

881
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,000
We're not apologizing.

882
00:36:46,080 --> 00:36:46,880
Deputy Mayor Luo.

883
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:49,360
Deputy Mayor Luo.

884
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:52,040
Old Mr. Xuan and Xuan Yan are here.

885
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:01,800
I designed this Xuan paper notebook.

886
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:04,280
The quality standards are admittedly quite high.

887
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,080
But to put it another way,

888
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,440
as long as our quality passes muster,

889
00:37:08,640 --> 00:37:10,360
every household will have food.

890
00:37:10,680 --> 00:37:13,560
If even one workshop fails on quality,

891
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:15,560
the whole deal collapses immediately.

892
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:18,240
It's just a notebook.

893
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:19,480
Why make it so well?

894
00:37:19,680 --> 00:37:21,160
Are we passing it down to future generations?

895
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:22,200
Exactly.

896
00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:25,800
Will it become a treasured antique?

897
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:27,160
What a joke.

898
00:37:27,160 --> 00:37:28,120
Brother Erhu.

899
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:31,040
Let's be reasonable, no need to bicker.

900
00:37:32,120 --> 00:37:33,360
Say what you will, we papermakers

901
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:34,840
count as half-cultured folk too.

902
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:37,040
Don't mistake ignorance for bravery.

903
00:37:39,240 --> 00:37:41,720
Technically, since I designed this,

904
00:37:41,720 --> 00:37:43,920
I have the right to decide who gets in.

905
00:37:44,160 --> 00:37:46,240
But everyone here today is my elder.

906
00:37:46,240 --> 00:37:47,080
So some things

907
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:49,640
my father should be the one to say.

908
00:37:50,680 --> 00:37:51,160
Dad.

909
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:53,560
I came over here today

910
00:37:53,760 --> 00:37:54,960
to say just three things.

911
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:56,720
Then I'll be on my way.

912
00:37:57,400 --> 00:37:58,320
First,

913
00:38:00,200 --> 00:38:02,360
about these Xuan paper notebooks,

914
00:38:03,040 --> 00:38:04,480
whoever's willing to make them,

915
00:38:04,680 --> 00:38:06,560
the orders will be shared evenly.

916
00:38:09,320 --> 00:38:11,920
Second, we can share the work,

917
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:14,320
but we can't ruin our reputation,

918
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:16,000
or fail our ancestors.

919
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:17,680
On this point,

920
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,840
I, Xuan Yongnian, take it very seriously.

921
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:22,240
And I hope all of you do too.

922
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:24,720
Also, we absolutely cannot let down

923
00:38:25,400 --> 00:38:27,160
Secretary Peng and Lin Yiran,

924
00:38:27,360 --> 00:38:29,680
after all the effort they've put in.

925
00:38:32,920 --> 00:38:33,720
Erhu.

926
00:38:35,520 --> 00:38:36,880
I know your ancestors,

927
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,720
back in the late Qing and Republican era,

928
00:38:39,240 --> 00:38:41,880
had quite the glorious run for years.

929
00:38:42,080 --> 00:38:44,200
Your paper company reached Shanghai, Guangzhou,

930
00:38:44,200 --> 00:38:45,560
Hong Kong, China, and Southeast Asia.

931
00:38:45,640 --> 00:38:47,160
Our Xuan family and your family

932
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,640
had a brotherly alliance,

933
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:50,880
supporting each other through it all.

934
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:54,400
We all eat from the bowl our ancestors gave us.

935
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:58,640
Don't smash that bowl.

936
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:04,360
That would shame our ancestors,

937
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:06,760
and even more so, our descendants.

938
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:09,640
Uncle Xuan.

939
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:12,480
And one last thing,

940
00:39:13,680 --> 00:39:16,400
Please stop giving Lin Yiran a hard time.

941
00:39:16,440 --> 00:39:18,160
She's just a young woman.

942
00:39:18,440 --> 00:39:20,080
She gave up her own future

943
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:21,920
to come back home and build up our town.

944
00:39:22,560 --> 00:39:25,720
We all need to act with a conscience.

945
00:39:26,080 --> 00:39:27,920
Everyone here is a grown man.

946
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:30,400
Out there, you're all respected figures.

947
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:33,040
Do your work well,

948
00:39:33,240 --> 00:39:36,880
and don't disgrace the town. That matters.

949
00:39:44,240 --> 00:39:46,160
That's all I have to say. Thank you.

950
00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:51,160
Sir.

951
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:54,160
Thank you so much this time.

952
00:39:54,240 --> 00:39:55,160
Thanks to you,

953
00:39:55,160 --> 00:39:56,680
you helped us settle a major matter.

954
00:39:56,680 --> 00:39:57,640
No, no, no.

955
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:07,600
Brother Erhu.

956
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,920
Once this job is done,

957
00:40:10,520 --> 00:40:12,560
maybe you'll do fewer shady things too.

958
00:40:51,040 --> 00:40:54,400
I really don't know about this caregiver Xiao Wang.

959
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:56,200
Who is she actually taking care of?

960
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:59,280
She only moves when you nag her.

961
00:40:59,920 --> 00:41:02,240
She's got zero common sense.

962
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:05,440
Always thinks she knows best.

963
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:08,320
Acts like she knows more than the doctor.

964
00:41:10,720 --> 00:41:12,840
Since you got sick until now,

965
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:14,520
we've already gone through six caregivers.

966
00:41:14,520 --> 00:41:16,040
What's the point of all this?

967
00:41:16,560 --> 00:41:18,000
People treat each other mutually.

968
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,840
Treat her well, she'll treat you well.

969
00:41:20,560 --> 00:41:22,440
In the end, isn't it for your own good?

970
00:41:23,040 --> 00:41:24,440
No matter how well you treat her,

971
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:25,560
it's just the same in the end.

972
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:28,040
If family is watching at home,

973
00:41:28,040 --> 00:41:29,160
things would be much better.

974
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,560
When the tiger's away from the mountain,

975
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:34,760
the monkey crowns himself king.

976
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:38,000
Anyway, if we replace Xiao Wang again,

977
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,480
I really don't know who else to find.

978
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,640
Figure it out yourself.

979
00:41:42,040 --> 00:41:43,160
Then forget the treatment.

980
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,200
Let's just go home.

981
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:55,000
No, if you ask me,

982
00:41:55,200 --> 00:41:57,120
Master is just too soft-hearted.

983
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:58,040
If it were me,

984
00:41:58,040 --> 00:41:59,840
whoever wants to make a fuss can go ahead.

985
00:42:00,160 --> 00:42:01,680
Once the money's earned

986
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:03,960
and in your own pocket, that's what's real.

987
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:07,080
Master doesn't want to put them in a bind.

988
00:42:07,200 --> 00:42:08,560
They're helping us.

989
00:42:08,640 --> 00:42:10,000
Help? Have they really helped?

990
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:11,440
I'm telling you, if the factory goes under,

991
00:42:11,440 --> 00:42:12,640
let's see who'd care about you.

992
00:42:12,640 --> 00:42:13,960
Worry about what concerns you.

993
00:42:14,360 --> 00:42:16,920
What doesn't concern you, don't butt in.

994
00:42:17,520 --> 00:42:18,120
Look at this,

995
00:42:18,120 --> 00:42:19,640
another one talking big with no skin in the game.

996
00:42:19,920 --> 00:42:21,080
You're a lonely old bachelor.

997
00:42:21,080 --> 00:42:22,400
Just you to feed, no family to worry about.

998
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:23,960
You shouldn't talk to your elders like that.

999
00:42:24,240 --> 00:42:24,760
Exactly.

1000
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:26,400
Which word of mine was wrong?

1001
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:27,080
Disrespecting elders,

1002
00:42:27,080 --> 00:42:28,240
that's what's wrong with how you speak.

1003
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:29,400
My savings for a wife are all gone.

1004
00:42:29,840 --> 00:42:31,160
Don't hit people!

1005
00:42:31,160 --> 00:42:32,320
Don't fight!

1006
00:42:32,920 --> 00:42:33,840
Hurry, come pull them apart!

1007
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:38,400
Beanpole!

1008
00:42:41,520 --> 00:42:42,200
Stop fighting!

1009
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:43,560
Stop it! Stop it!

1010
00:42:48,200 --> 00:42:48,920
Don't fight anymore!

1011
00:42:48,920 --> 00:42:49,400
He's hitting people!

1012
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:49,920
Stop fighting!

1013
00:42:49,920 --> 00:42:50,520
What are you guys doing?

1014
00:42:50,720 --> 00:42:51,760
Putting on a show, huh?

1015
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:53,160
You're putting on an act, right?

1016
00:42:53,160 --> 00:42:54,080
Enough!

1017
00:42:54,080 --> 00:42:55,520
What are you doing? What are you doing?

1018
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:56,040
You!

1019
00:42:56,040 --> 00:42:57,560
Get out of the way! Get lost!

1020
00:42:57,760 --> 00:42:58,760
Go on, hit me! Hit me!

1021
00:42:58,760 --> 00:42:59,440
You hit me!
